OL,3,CMan charged with murder after death of
OL,4,C74-year-old grandad
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man from Cwmbran has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with murder following the
OL,8,Fdeath of a 74-year-old man from
OL,9,FTrevethin, in Torfaen.
OL,11,FThe man, who was also charged with
OL,12,Fthreats to kill and harassment, is set
OL,13,Fto appear at Newport Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt on Monday (27 April).
OL,16,FNicholas 'Brian' Parfitt was
OL,17,Fpronounced dead at an address on
OL,18,FBythway Road in Trevethin at
OL,19,Fapproximately 4:55pm on Thursday, 23
OL,20,FApril.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
