PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777453578
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after death of
OL,4,C74-year-old grandad
OL,6,FHe was found with serious injuries.
OL,7,FBoth the Welsh Ambulance Service and
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Air Ambulance attended the
OL,9,Fproperty.
OL,11,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Shelly
OL,13,FComley said: "We understand that there
OL,14,Fhas been a great deal of interest in
OL,15,Fthis investigation.
OL,17,F"We ask that people consider how their
OL,18,Flanguage, especially comments made
OL,19,Fonline, could impact our ability to
OL,20,Fbring anyone found to have committed a
OL,21,Fcriminal offence to justice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
