PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1777453578
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after death of
OL,4,C74-year-old grandad
OL,6,F"Officers will remain in the area as
OL,7,Four enquiries continue, so if anyone
OL,8,Fhas any information please speak to
OL,9,Four officers or contact us in the
OL,10,Fusual way."
OL,12,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,13,Fcontact Gwent Police.
OL,15,FIn a previous statement, Mr Parfitt's
OL,16,Ffamily paid tribute to him. They said:
OL,17,F"Brian's passing has been a shock to
OL,18,Fboth the family and the community.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
